/* Distribution of gold medalists with age */
 
%sql
 
select count(Medal) as Medals, Age from athlete_events where Medal = 'Gold' group by Age order by Age desc;

/* women medals per edition in summer season in games */
 
select count(Medal) as Medals, Year from athlete_events where sex = 'F' and Season = 'Summer' and Medal in ('Bronze', 'Gold' , 'Silver') group by Year order by Year;
